Test-Run-Plugin-ColorSummary

This plugin allows Test::Run to make color the summary line in one color
on success and in a different color on failure. It uses the Term::ANSIColor
module for that.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


